This really isn=E2=80=99t an entity that was created to be a consumer tech =
company, and not just because of its weird corporate structure; Friedman=E2=
=80=99s point is that the culture wasn=E2=80=99t that of a consumer tech co=
mpany either. This is the first reason why I thought last week=E2=80=99s la=
unch of ChatGPT plugins was so important: to me it signaled a major shift i=
